He's great. Really loves the material, wants students to do well and sets up the class so that students will do well. The class was fun as well, definitely would take it again.

great class to take to learn. Don't take it as a bird class. There is a lot of work in this class but that gives the opportunity to get a better grade in the end. unbelievable prof! loved his class and he was super helpful

Jordan is very approachable and sincerely cares for his students and their progress in his courses. Sometimes the lectures can get a little boring, but if you read all the books you will do well! I love the creative response instead of a mid-term paper. Jordan's passion for the material makes the course interesting and fun. Pro tip: BUY THE BOOKS AND WATCH THE MOVIES. Jordan uses ALL the material he asks for. Also attend the lectures, if you do this course is easy and you'll be glad you did.

One of the most helpful, comprehensive, understanding and kindest professors you will encounter. He goes way above and beyond what you would expect of a professor and treats his students with a level of respect and dedication that is really rare and something special.
